# Better Auth signing secret. OPTIONAL.
#
# If unset, the worker auto-generates one and stores it in the D1 `settings` table —
# so the Deploy-to-Cloudflare button works with zero configuration. Set this explicitly
# for production (e.g. `wrangler secret put BETTER_AUTH_SECRET`) if you want to control
# the secret or rotate it. A set env value always wins over the stored fallback.
#
# Generate one with: openssl rand -base64 32
BETTER_AUTH_SECRET=
